version_description:
-FPP Mode 
Loot and shoot like never before. Get up close to the action with the new first-person mode and enjoy a truly immersive experience. What changes will the new mode bring to the battlefield? What new strategies will you adopt? Gear up and jump in to find out.

-Large Indoor Map
The battle for wealth has moved indoors! Be careful! There may be an enemy ambush around every corner. Sieges, bunker combat, indoor assaults, and balls-to-the-wall defense. The new map is set to bring you a new and thrilling combat experience. 

-Weapon Skins, DIY Customization
New custom weapon skins; jungle, desert, stripes, digital and others more than 10 kinds of styles, plus special time-limited skins for the holidays. With a wealth of accessories and attachments to modify your weapons, be sure to always look your best on the battlefield!
